  Scenario: Introspect types
    When I send the following GraphQL request:
    """
    {
      __type(name: "Mutation") {
        fields {
          name
          description
          type {
            name
            kind
          }
          args {
            name
            type {
              name
              kind
              ofType {
                name
                kind
              }
            }
          }
